{
  "stem": "16930.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was , I mean, maybe arithmetic or English, sort of in relation to that-- in relation to that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I also joined a boys club in London, the Jewish boys' clubs in London, where I also did boxing and played ping-pong, [LAUGHS] and whatever they do there, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so that-- what I was into.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was the other boy what I was living with was not into those things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I also joined B'nai Akiva.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And B'nai Akiva had meetings every Shabbos, which means every Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had meetings.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and so that kept my-- my-- I had a pretty full plate, going-- having a full-time work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in those days, a job was maybe-- even when I was 14 years old, was more than 40 hours.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how many more than 40 hours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, it wasn't just a 40 hour, like it now in America, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were more hours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the kid then, a 14-year-old kid, wasn't a child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, a 14-year-old kid was already somebody who was either learning a trade or making a living.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a different atmosphere, a different evaluation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in a sense, I never got to be a teenager where you do nothing but go to school and drive a car and whatever-- they have promiscuous sex.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never got into these things, these fun things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was pretty well more of a-- and I had a lot of ideology, was quite motivated by ideology, especially from-- I got it from the Akiva towards Israel.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a B'nai Akiva, so there was a part of Mizrachi.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the ideology was always war time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And nobody could go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ideology was to go to Israel or be involved with Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
